 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779242661}, {"pid": 868716440, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 10:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868715606,45974302,5455]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65329649]zippo578[/uid] (2026-05-20 10:01):[/b]<br/><br/>黄下白上<br/>放量[/quote]<br/>因为打到很多板块的临界点了  比如各种金属类 距离我上次说等沃什后连跌一周  谁也扛不住", "lou": 2646, "content_length": 83, "reply_to": 868715606, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779242832}, {"pid": 868716758, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 10:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868716452,45974302,5456]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=34849073]雪ノ下雪乃[/uid] (2026-05-20 10:07):[/b]<br/><br/>这里还是B反吧，C杀的时候应该有最后一次加仓的机会[s:ac:瞎][/quote]<br/>很多板块B反但是没反  他们敢C杀加仓?换你 你最多不割肉  你敢加仓？", "lou": 2647, "content_length": 64, "reply_to": 868716452, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779242962}, {"pid": 868717363, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 10:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868717159,45974302,5457]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=37905679]Nightknightm[/uid] (2026-05-20 10:11):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大  那就是等他们来 半导体加速冲顶 然后我们走 对吧[/quote]<br/>对  所以我就等什么时候大减而已。不会再买了", "lou": 2648, "content_length": 45, "reply_to": 868717159, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779243183}, {"pid": 868717673, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 46, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 10:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868717378,45974302,5458]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66731212]Amupter[/uid] (2026-05-20 10:13):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，稀土个股走势是不是要到下面箱体底部去了，最近这波下跌量不少[/quote]<br/>我知道  所以我不是减了么。直接避开七天连杀 这还不行吗", "lou": 2649, "content_length": 55, "reply_to"