 "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "上个月我预判了本月上半月是688比较强<br/>接下来我判断柚子抱团情绪会比较强，是超短的行情<br/>我谨慎参与。", "lou": 2654, "content_length": 93, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779252829}, {"pid": 868742639, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 27, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 12:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868742343,45974302,5481]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64648193]一生一股绊倒铁盒[/uid] (2026-05-20 12:54):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，能透露下今天收盘打算多少仓位吗[s:ac:羡慕][/quote]<br/>我说了 我现在的仓位没什么意义 我目前都是70%仓位左右 <br/>我出去的仓位自然有我的用处。我提现了", "lou": 2655, "content_length": 90, "reply_to": 868742343, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779253049}, {"pid": 868743545, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 70, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 13:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "看吧  那些散户割肉金属去科技<br/>现在金属拉起来了。。。。。", "lou": 2656, "content_length": 52, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779253564}, {"pid": 868743829, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 13:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868743705,45974302,5482]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=11609837]3621gg[/uid] (2026-05-20 13:07):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:a2:囧]然后认错再买回去？在被割一刀，这也太惨了吧。。。[/quote]<br/>不管是回去被一刀  还是犹豫两边都不买  或者两边都买  都是个煎熬", "lou": 2657, "content_length": 61, "reply_to": 868743705, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779253724}, {"pid": 868744204, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 42, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-20 13:11", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=868743878,45974302,5483]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42719239]我呆毛王天下第一[/uid] (2026-05-20 13:09):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大狼大，想请教下拉光诱多的预期还在嘛，前几天埋伏了点通信ETF[s:ac:怕]看这几天还没咋动，还是说诱多是用二线弹性票来诱，ETF不太能看呀[/quote]<br/>在", "lou": 2658, "content_length": 7, "reply